  demon was really only a turtle, but the princes had never seen a turtle before.
  To calm {+their-(their / his)|145} fears, the king ordered his servants to go capture
  the demon and bring {+it-(them / it)|144} to the palace. When they had done so,
  {+he-(he / she)|144} ordered them to kill the demon.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"We should throw it
  into the fire!\\\" shouted one of the princes.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"We should smash it with a
  hammer!\\\" shouted the other prince.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe king''s advisers also shouted out
